Pooling the Poles

Pooled polls of intended voting at parliamentary elections in Poland, Friday 14 January.

Data from CBOS, IBRIS, Kantar, Pollster, Research Partner, Social Changes and United Surveys.

Latest estimates


Figures shown in white are median estimates of support per party. Undecided voters are excluded.
